data.description: Come see this spacious home in the sought after neighborhood of Montclair. This 4 bedroom / 2 1/2 bath home is on a corner lot and ready for its new family. As you enter this home, you are greeted with a spacious foyer and a formal living and dining room on either side. Moving forward into the living area, you are greeted with a large family room with fireplace and large kitchen. True Open concept. Eat in kitchen, large walk-in pantry, half bath and access to the newly stained large deck and back yard, great for friends and family gatherings. Upstairs boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths including an extra-large master bedroom and bath with double walk-in closets. Maintenance on the home include Roof 2023, all new carpet upstairs, freshly painted interior, and the septic tank cleaned and serviced 2022. This home won't last!! Please come see us!!!
